#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:2
msgid "NIXL"
msgstr "NIXL"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:4
msgid ""
"NIXL-based persistent storage — the primary production L2 backend, using "
"NIXL (NVIDIA Interconnect Library) for high-performance storage I/O. Two "
"adapter types share this backend:"
msgstr "基于 NIXL 的持久存储 — 主要的生产 L2 后端，使用 NIXL（NVIDIA 互连库）进行高性能存储 I/O。两种适配器类型共享此后端："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:8
msgid ""
"``nixl_store`` — a fixed pool of storage descriptors pre-allocated at "
"init."
msgstr "``nixl_store`` — 在初始化时预分配的固定存储描述符池。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:9
msgid ""
"``nixl_store_dynamic`` — opens and registers files per operation, adding "
"persist/recover across restarts and removing the open-file-descriptor "
"limit."
msgstr "``nixl_store_dynamic`` — 每次操作时动态打开并注册文件，支持跨重启的持久化/恢复，并消除打开文件描述符数量的限制。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:13
msgid "Static pool — ``nixl_store``"
msgstr "静态池 — ``nixl_store``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:15
msgid ""
"The primary production adapter. Pre-allocates a pool of storage "
"descriptors at initialization."
msgstr "主要的生产适配器。在初始化时预分配一组存储描述符池。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:18
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:92
msgid "**Required fields:**"
msgstr "**必填字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:20
msgid ""
"``backend``: Storage backend -- one of ``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, "
"``HF3FS``, ``OBJ``, ``AZURE_BLOB``."
msgstr "``backend``: 存储后端 -- 以下之一：``POSIX``、``GDS``、``GDS_MT``、``HF3FS``、``OBJ``、``AZURE_BLOB``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:22
msgid ""
"``pool_size``: Number of storage descriptors to pre-allocate (must be > "
"0)."
msgstr "``pool_size``: 预分配的存储描述符数量（必须大于 0）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:24
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:97
msgid "**Backend-specific parameters (``backend_params``):**"
msgstr "**后端特定参数 (``backend_params``):**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:26
msgid "File-based backends (``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, ``POSIX``, ``HF3FS``) require:"
msgstr "基于文件的后端（``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, ``POSIX``, ``HF3FS``）需要："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:28
msgid "``file_path``: Directory path for storing L2 data."
msgstr "``file_path``: 存储 L2 数据的目录路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:29
msgid ""
"``use_direct_io``: ``\"true\"`` or ``\"false\"`` -- whether to use direct"
" I/O."
msgstr "``use_direct_io``: ``\"true\"`` 或 ``\"false\"`` -- 是否使用直接 I/O。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:31
msgid ""
"The ``OBJ`` and ``AZURE_BLOB`` backends (object stores) do not require "
"``file_path``."
msgstr "``OBJ`` 和 ``AZURE_BLOB`` 后端（对象存储）不需要 ``file_path``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:33
msgid "**Backend descriptions:**"
msgstr "**后端描述：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:39
msgid "Backend"
msgstr "后端"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:40
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:41
msgid "``POSIX``"
msgstr "``POSIX``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:42
msgid "Standard POSIX file I/O.  Works on any file system.  No direct I/O."
msgstr "标准 POSIX 文件 I/O。适用于任何文件系统。无直接 I/O。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:43
msgid "``GDS``"
msgstr "``GDS``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:44
msgid ""
"NVIDIA GPU Direct Storage.  Enables direct GPU-to-storage transfers "
"bypassing the CPU.  Requires NVMe SSDs with GDS support."
msgstr "NVIDIA GPU 直接存储。启用直接的 GPU 到存储传输，绕过 CPU。需要支持 GDS 的 NVMe SSD。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:46
msgid "``GDS_MT``"
msgstr "``GDS_MT``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:47
msgid "Multi-threaded variant of GDS for higher throughput."
msgstr "GDS 的多线程变体，以提高吞吐量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:48
msgid "``HF3FS``"
msgstr "``HF3FS``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:49
msgid "Shared file system backend (e.g., for distributed/networked storage)."
msgstr "共享文件系统后端（例如，用于分布式/网络存储）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:50
msgid "``OBJ``"
msgstr "``OBJ``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:51
msgid "Object store backend.  No local file path required."
msgstr "对象存储后端。无需本地文件路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:52
msgid "``AZURE_BLOB``"
msgstr "``AZURE_BLOB``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:53
msgid "Object store backend for Azure Blob Storage.  No local file path required."
msgstr "Azure Blob Storage 的对象存储后端。无需本地文件路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:55
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:114
msgid "**Configuration examples:**"
msgstr "**配置示例：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:78
msgid "Dynamic (persist / recover) — ``nixl_store_dynamic``"
msgstr "动态（持久/恢复） — ``nixl_store_dynamic``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:80
msgid ""
"A dynamic variant of the NIXL adapter that opens and registers files per-"
"operation instead of pre-allocating them at init. This enables:"
msgstr "NIXL 适配器的动态变体，按操作打开和注册文件，而不是在初始化时预分配。该变体支持以下功能："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:83
msgid "**Persist/recover** -- cached KV metadata survives restarts."
msgstr "**持久化/恢复** -- 缓存的 KV 元数据在重启后仍然存在。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:84
msgid ""
"**No fd limits** -- files are opened and closed per transfer, so the "
"cache can grow beyond OS open-file-descriptor limits."
msgstr "**无文件描述符限制** -- 文件在每次传输时打开和关闭，因此缓存可以超出操作系统的打开文件描述符限制。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:89
msgid ""
"Only file-based backends are supported (``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, "
"``HF3FS``). The ``OBJ`` and ``AZURE_BLOB`` backends are not supported "
"yet."
msgstr "仅支持基于文件的后端（``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, ``HF3FS``）。``OBJ`` 和 ``AZURE_BLOB`` 后端尚不支持。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:94
msgid ""
"``backend``: Storage backend -- one of ``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, "
"``HF3FS``."
msgstr "``backend``: 存储后端 -- 以下之一：``POSIX``、``GDS``、``GDS_MT``、``HF3FS``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:99
msgid "``file_path``: Directory path for storing L2 data files."
msgstr "``file_path``: 存储 L2 数据文件的目录路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:100
msgid "``use_direct_io``: ``\"true\"`` or ``\"false\"``."
msgstr "``use_direct_io``: ``\"true\"`` 或 ``\"false\"``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:101
msgid ""
"``max_capacity_gb``: Maximum storage capacity in GB. The adapter rejects "
"stores when this limit is reached. Required for the eviction controller "
"to compute usage."
msgstr "``max_capacity_gb``: 最大存储容量（以 GB 为单位）。当达到此限制时，适配器会拒绝存储。此项是逐出控制器计算使用情况所必需的。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:105
msgid "**Optional fields (for persist):**"
msgstr "**可选字段（用于持久化）：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:107
msgid ""
"``persist_enabled`` (bool, default ``true``): If ``true``, data files are"
" kept on disk at shutdown. If ``false``, all data files are deleted on "
"shutdown."
msgstr "``persist_enabled`` (bool, 默认 ``true``): 若为 ``true``，关闭时数据文件将保留在磁盘上。若为 ``false``，关闭时所有数据文件将被删除。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:111
msgid ""
"Lookup always checks secondary storage (disk) on miss and lazily "
"populates the in-memory index when a file is found."
msgstr "查找时，若未命中则始终回退到二级存储（磁盘）进行检查；找到文件后，惰性填充内存索引。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:127
msgid "**Persist / secondary lookup behaviour:**"
msgstr "**持久化 / 二级查找行为:**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:129
msgid ""
"On **shutdown**, the adapter keeps data files on disk by default "
"(``persist_enabled`` defaults to ``true``). If explicitly set to "
"``false``, all data files are deleted to avoid orphaned storage."
msgstr "在 **关闭** 时，适配器默认将数据文件保留在磁盘上（``persist_enabled`` 默认为 ``true``）。如果明确设置为 ``false``，则所有数据文件将被删除，以避免孤立存储。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/nixl.rst:132
msgid ""
"On **startup**, the in-memory index is empty. Every lookup miss falls "
"through to a secondary lookup on disk: if the deterministic file exists, "
"it is treated as a hit and the in-memory index is populated lazily from "
"the file size."
msgstr "在 **启动** 时，内存索引为空。每次查找未命中都会回退到磁盘上的二级查找：若对应的确定性文件存在，则视为命中，并根据文件大小惰性填充内存索引。"

